ing  <code>@interface MasterViewController : UIViewController &lt;NSURLSessionDelegate&gt;</code>  and I use this protocol method </p>  <pre><code>-(void)URLSession:(NSURLSession *)session downloadTask:(NSURLSessionDownloadTask *)downloadTask didFinishDownloadingToURL:(NSURL *)location </code></pre>  <p>But when I use the viewDidLoad, that code never get fire, jus in the IBAction, and I need it in the viewDidLoad. I try to explain as clear as i could, hoping anybody gave me any advice. Thanks in advance. </p>